_sText:
This map is running fullbright, and with no "Nodraw" textures, however I managed to pass 300 FPS, so no complains!!

This is a newer version of the first map I´ve ever created called sw_minitown_n3.. N for new

This is a very simple map! A small map, but funny to play, lot´s of hiding spots, including a great tower. if you have a sniper-rifle. A sewer system, or something like that. A hotel, a building a house, some cars. This map got it. Download it and rate it... however!! Remember that this is an improvement of my first map.

If you like it then put it up on your server, whatever... If you want to improve the map even more, please tell me first, or give me some creed!

Files: 

.BSP

.NAV

Some screenshots, .JPG

Download I say!
